text: Víctor Gutiérrez may refer to: * Víctor Gutiérrez (footballer) (born 1978), Mexican football player * Víctor Gutiérrez (water polo) (born 1991), Spanish water polo player * Víctor Manuel Gutiérrez (1922–1966), Guatemalan labour leader * Victor M. Gutierrez, a freelance writer who appeared on the U.S. tabloid television show "Hard Copy" to claim that there was a videotape of Michael Jackson molesting a boy, see 1993 child sexual abuse accusations against Michael Jackson.
title: Víctor Gutiérrez
